PN,30301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784854088
OL,3,C11-year-old girl is first UK patient
OL,4,Cto have gene therapy to halt sight loss
OL,6,FAn 11-year-old girl has become the
OL,7,Ffirst UK patient to have innovative
OL,8,Fgene therapy for a rare condition that
OL,9,Frobs children of their sight.
OL,11,FThe treatment, which had only been
OL,12,Fperformed on one other person in the
OL,13,Fworld, involves injecting healthy
OL,14,Fcopies of a gene directly into the eye.
OL,16,FCatherine L'Estrange, from North Acton
OL,17,Fin west London, is hopeful the move
OL,18,Fwill allow her to continue one of her
OL,19,Ffavourite hobbies ` reading books.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784854088
OL,3,C11-year-old girl is first UK patient
OL,4,Cto have gene therapy to halt sight loss
OL,6,FIf the therapy works, her sight will
OL,7,Fbe stabilised or may even improve,
OL,8,Faccording to the surgeon who treated
OL,9,Fher.
OL,11,FCatherine was diagnosed Bardet-Biedl
OL,12,Fsyndrome (BBS) when she was just a
OL,13,Fbaby.
OL,15,FThe condition is caused by mutations
OL,16,Fto one of 20 different genes and
OL,17,Fimpacts around one in 100,000 births
OL,18,Fin the UK, leaving patients blind by
OL,19,Ftheir late teens or early 20s.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784854088
OL,3,C11-year-old girl is first UK patient
OL,4,Cto have gene therapy to halt sight loss
OL,6,FAs well as vision loss, BBS can also
OL,7,Fcause kidney problems, learning
OL,8,Fdifficulties and obesity, and patients
OL,9,Fsometimes have extra fingers or toes.
OL,11,FThe gene therapy, developed by
OL,12,Fbiotechnology company MeiraGTx, was
OL,13,Fgiven to Catherine as part of an hour-
OL,14,Flong procedure at St Helier Hospital
OL,15,Fin March.
OL,17,FSurgeons removed the jelly inside her
OL,18,Feye and injected healthy copies of a
OL,19,Fgene into the retina, the light
OL,20,Fsensitive layer of tissue at the back
OL,21,Fof the eye.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784854088
OL,3,C11-year-old girl is first UK patient
OL,4,Cto have gene therapy to halt sight loss
OL,6,FIn people with BBS, small cells in the
OL,7,Fretina die, leading to blindness.
OL,9,FNeruban Kumaran, consultant eye
OL,10,Fsurgeon at Epsom and St Helier
OL,11,FUniversity Hospitals NHS Trust, told
OL,12,Fthe Press Association: "By giving a
OL,13,Fhealthy copy of the gene, it helps
OL,14,Fsave those cells, and the hope is to
OL,15,Feither stabilise or improve vision."
OL,26,@tD@XOUwD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784854088
OL,3,C11-year-old girl is first UK patient
OL,4,Cto have gene therapy to halt sight loss
OL,6,FCatherine said: "If this treatment
OL,7,Fworks, it will help me to carry on
OL,8,Fseeing things around me, and most of
OL,9,Fall I will be able to carry on reading
OL,10,Fbooks, which is one of my favourite
OL,11,Fthings to do."
OL,13,FHer father, Reverend Timothy
OL,14,FL'Estrange, said most children with
OL,15,FBBS do not get diagnosed until they
OL,16,Fare in primary school, but Catherine
OL,17,Fwas diagnosed at a few weeks old,
OL,18,Fallowing the family to plan her future.
OL,26,@nD@QOUsD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784854088
OL,3,C11-year-old girl is first UK patient
OL,4,Cto have gene therapy to halt sight loss
OL,6,F"Our policy was to develop her
OL,7,Findependence and resilience as much as
OL,8,Fpossible, ready for the inevitable
OL,9,Floss of her sight, which began with
OL,10,Fher becoming night-blind, then colour-
OL,11,Fblind, and continued with her losing
OL,12,Fher peripheral vision," he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784854088
OL,3,C11-year-old girl is first UK patient
OL,4,Cto have gene therapy to halt sight loss
OL,6,F"We were told that possible gene
OL,7,Ftherapy was many, many years away, and
OL,8,Fwas likely to arrive after Catherine
OL,9,Fhad entirely lost her sight ` so we
OL,10,Fwere surprised and delighted when we
OL,11,Flearned this treatment had become
OL,12,Favailable, and that Catherine would be
OL,13,Fone of the first patients in the world
OL,14,Fto receive it."
OL,16,FJust one of Catherine's eyes has been
OL,17,Ftreated with the new gene therapy,
OL,18,Fwith the team now waiting to see the
OL,19,Fresults.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784854088
OL,3,C11-year-old girl is first UK patient
OL,4,Cto have gene therapy to halt sight loss
OL,6,FThe treatment is designed specifically
OL,7,Ffor patients with a BBS10 gene
OL,8,Fmutation, which is one of the most
OL,9,Fcommon among BBS patients.
OL,11,FThe team at St Helier worked with
OL,12,Fexperts at Great Ormond Street and
OL,13,FMoorfields Eye Hospital to identify
OL,14,Feligible patients, as youngsters with
OL,15,FBBS have genetic tests to pinpoint
OL,16,Fwhich of the 20 genes is mutated based
OL,17,Fon their symptoms.
OL,19,FOnly one other person ` a 17-year-old
OL,20,Fgirl from Canada ` had received the
OL,21,Ftreatment before Catherine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784854088
OL,3,C11-year-old girl is first UK patient
OL,4,Cto have gene therapy to halt sight loss
OL,6,FHer procedure took place at St Helier
OL,7,Fin August last year.
OL,9,FThe parents of the girl, who wishes to
OL,10,Fremain anonymous, said: "This
OL,11,Ftreatment has given our daughter a
OL,12,Fprecious chance to preserve her
OL,13,Fvision, and we hope it will become a
OL,14,Flife-changing therapy for children
OL,15,Fwith BBS10 all over the world."
OL,17,FSince Catherine, the procedure has
OL,18,Falso been performed on one other
OL,19,Fyounger child with BBS.
OL,26,@rD@YOUwD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784854088
OL,3,C11-year-old girl is first UK patient
OL,4,Cto have gene therapy to halt sight loss
OL,6,FAfter having the therapy, patients are
OL,7,Fseen in clinic and have various sight
OL,8,Ftests, such as reading from a chart
OL,9,Fand identifying different shades of
OL,10,Fcolours.
OL,12,FMr Kumaran said some have already said
OL,13,Ftheir vision is better in dim light
OL,14,Fand the feedback so far has been
OL,15,Fpositive, though it will take years
OL,16,Fbefore the full results are known.
OL,18,F"There is a hope that it may improve
OL,19,Fvision slightly, but it's difficult to
OL,20,Fsay," he told PA.
OL,26,@zD@AOU|D@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784854088
OL,3,C11-year-old girl is first UK patient
OL,4,Cto have gene therapy to halt sight loss
OL,6,F"It's not going to leave someone with
OL,7,Fperfect vision. But the hope is to
OL,8,Fstabilise and/or improve vision. Only
OL,9,Ftime will tell.
OL,11,F"There's been some very positive
OL,12,Ffeedback from a mixture of the
OL,13,Fpatients and the families that suggest
OL,14,Ftheir vision may be better.
OL,16,F"Early reports from the families have
OL,17,Fbeen very promising, and it gives us
OL,18,Flots of hope. But in practice, it will
OL,19,Ftake many years before we're sure."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU{D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784854088
OL,3,C11-year-old girl is first UK patient
OL,4,Cto have gene therapy to halt sight loss
OL,6,FReverend L'Estrange said: "Our whole
OL,7,Ffamily has been so grateful for the
OL,8,Fopportunity to save Catherine's vision
OL,9,F` it will be absolutely life-changing
OL,10,Ffor her to retain any vision at all."
OL,12,FMr Kumaran is hopeful there will be
OL,13,Fother children out there eligible for
OL,14,Fthe therapy, as well as babies who
OL,15,Fhave not even been born yet.
OL,26,@nD@[OUrD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784854088
OL,3,C11-year-old girl is first UK patient
OL,4,Cto have gene therapy to halt sight loss
OL,6,FHe told PA it has been a "real honour"
OL,7,Fto have the opportunity to help these
OL,8,Fchildren, adding: "These families and
OL,9,Fthe children have a lot of
OL,10,Fdifficulties as it is, just because of
OL,11,Fall the other conditions they're
OL,12,Faffected by.
OL,14,F"And one of the things that causes a
OL,15,Flot of anxiety is the worry that these
OL,16,Fchildren lose vision and possibly lose
OL,17,Ftheir independence.
OL,26,@nD@ZOUnD@fO]pD@SOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784854088
OL,3,C11-year-old girl is first UK patient
OL,4,Cto have gene therapy to halt sight loss
OL,6,F"There's no other treatment for this,
OL,7,Fand so the opportunity to protect
OL,8,Fvision or improve vision, or give them
OL,9,Fhope that they won't lose their vision
OL,10,Fand they can maintain that
OL,11,Findependence, it really means a lot."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784854088
OL,3,C11-year-old girl is first UK patient
OL,4,Cto have gene therapy to halt sight loss
OL,6,FMat Shaw, chief executive of St
OL,7,FGeorge's, Epsom and St Helier
OL,8,FHospitals Group, said: "As a father, I
OL,9,Fcan't imagine how it feels to watch
OL,10,Fyour child slowly go blind, and I'm so
OL,11,Fproud that our teams are offering hope
OL,12,Fto these children and their families,
OL,13,Fwhich aims to stop childhood blindness
OL,14,Fin its tracks and change what's
OL,15,Fpossible for the future of children
OL,16,Fwith this devastating condition."
OL,26,@pD@XOUxD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/15
